	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=6007><span id= >Kilroth</span></a><br><span id=notbold>120 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default [2.11]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>Anyone got anything important like, what the accual haste % is?<br><br>While this item is great for ANY class most people would give it to the tanks first, because most people who would be getting the quest item would be in guild groups. However it is up to the accual group doing the killing to distribute their loot. I dont get why everyone posts irrelevent information, not to sound like a hippocrit, couse i have done it a couple times. But, i doubt that anyone who can accually get this would be reading all these posts about how they should distribute their loot.</p>&nbsp;<br></td></td></tr>
